data.lettercontent: Hello. I am a fan from Shaanxi, China. I know you must know China, but Shaanxi may not be known to you, but it doesn't matter. Just remember that I am your Chinese fan and there are many people who love you in China. Although you may not see this letter, I still want to write to you. From the first time I saw you to now, I thought you were a very cold person from the beginning, but now I think you are cute and responsible. It didn't take a long time, I don't know why, but I have always vaguely felt that you are a very easy to get along with. After getting to know you, sometimes I will see your responsible side, and sometimes I will see you and your members acting coquettishly. The ever-changing nature of you makes me feel that you are a person worth being loved, I hope you and your members can be healthy and happy every day in the future. Please remember me, I will always be behind you. As long as you turn your head, you can see me. Don't worry about me walking away. I will always be there and support you. Fighting!
data.user_agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/112.0.0.0 Safari/537.36

data.lettercontent:
Hi OX~,

 I didn’t know these letters were a thing until just a few 
minutes ago, but I’m grateful to For X that put this together so 
we can talk. First of all. I love watching all of you guys’ tik toks 
and seeing your pictures on instagram and Twitter, it brings 
me happiness to see you guys living your best life. Also 
congratulations on your performance! I was cheering you guys 
on and ‘Dream’ is beautiful! I can’t wait to see what else you 
guys have in store for us and I’ll be sure to cheer y’all on then 
as well. It’s been a while right? I remember when you guys 
came to San Antonio, it was my first time seeing you but I 
know it definitely won’t be the last so I’ll wait for you 
patiently:). I’ve have an Omega X bracelet I made when you 
guys came here, and I’ve never took it off since, not even 
once. I can’t put into words how much I miss you but also even 
more impossible to describe is how much I am so proud of you 
all. Your strength is unmatched and please always know I am 
here to protect you and be the light at the end of the tunnel. I 
don’t want to ramble any longer haha but thank you for 
reading this letter, it means a lot. I love y’all so so so much and 
let’s talk again soon. 



-Sabryna
data.user_agent: Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/110.0.0.0 Safari/537.36

data.lettercontent:
I'm a 누나 FORX, and I just want to tell you guys that you are 
really important to me. You were my first Kpop concert ever. 
I'm from Guadalajara, México, you're first stop on the last 
tour. I hope, besides everything, you could feel the love this 
city and Mexico has for you. I got you a doll that is very 
representative of Mexico, called Doctor Simi, I hope the 
Mexican staff have sent them to you. 
Last week I watch your performance at HMA, and You don't have 
idea how proud I am of you guys. You deserve the best in this 
world. 
I Love you so so much! I hope to see you again!! Lots of love 
from Mexico!!
